{"tid":210374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太變態】3少年欺凌女同學 摸下體笑住影相","createTime":"2017-04-21T01:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T09:32:51.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"087bfb7caa9a46efa3211125c86ab171394d4a75","tid":210374,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492735953_7318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492735953_7318.jpg&h=963ea2cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地網上近日熱傳一輯中學女生遭欺凌的照片。相中共有3男1女，全部穿着校服，3名男生將女生拖進廁所，並脫下褲子，其中1名男生摸她的下體。有網民指，此事發生於甘肅慶陽市第四中學。<br />\n<br />\n昨日中午，慶陽市西峯區委外宣辦發佈通佈，慶陽四中於本月11日中午12時放學後，發生一宗欺凌事件，公安機關已對組織、脅迫的主要疑犯刑事拘留，其餘涉案疑犯則被處行政拘留，紀檢監察機關亦已對教育主管部門、涉事學校相關負責人嚴肅問責。同時，正安排專家對受害人及其家長進行情緒疏導和心理輔導。<br />\n通報並呼籲，因事件涉及未成年人，網民勿轉發相關照片，否則將被依法依規追究責任。"},{"pid":"0df06053d03683de323757fc4ece15a810bd3ba3","tid":210374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b97b94bd9505b5d3c74f8a8fbfb8954ea4ec81","tid":210374,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"冇後台既就死撚梗啦"},{"pid":"bba178de5806ed6d89dc583d716c3f8d98440a46","tid":210374,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"支那新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9a52d4ae762b631f1e3f65b27427dfadadb0a8","tid":210374,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"無後台無錢<br />\n<br />\nmola mola"}]}